description:
It’s the last day. After Matt has one more day of fun with the girls, its time to move on. A beautiful sunrise is the perfect setting for a morning flogging. Donna and Jenni are staked out and Donna is made to lick Jenni for most of the afternoon. Darling is tied to a tree but it is not your ordinary tie–this one comes with an anal hook. Late in the afternoon the Sgt. and Matt have all four girls spread out and staked. After forcing orgasms on all of them it is time to move on. Matt and the Sgt take to the road. Warning: Do not hitchhike in CABO, you never know who will pick you up.
We hope you enjoyed our CABO series; it is intended to be watched all at one time, so if you get the chance, please check it out this way. We added some outtakes, a deleted scene, and some other goodies. Enjoy the first day of summer!
title: CABO, the Return. Part 10 - the Finale.
